  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to determine the prevalence of latent tuberculosis infection
      among injecting drug users and to conduct randomized controlled trial to evaluate a case
      management intervention aimed at increasing TB screening and treatment entry among injecting
      drug users referred from a methadone drug treatment program in Estonia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
